Eren and his companions in the 104th are assigned to the newly-formed Levi Squad, whose assignment is to keep Eren and Historia safe given Eren's newly-discovered power and Historia's knowledge and pedigree. Levi and Erwin have good reason to be concerned, because the priest of the Church that Hanji had hidden away was found tortured to death, making it clear that the Military Police are involved with the cover-up. Things get more harrowing when the MPs make a move on Erwin and the Levi Squad narrowly avoids capture. Eren is also having problems with his Titan transformation, and a deadly killer has been hired to secure Eren and Historia, one Levi knows all too well from his youth.
(Source: Anime News Network)

Timid Tadano is a total wallflower, and thats just the way he likes it. But all that changes when he finds himself alone in a classroom on the first day of high school with the legendary Komi. He quickly realizes she isnt aloofshes just super awkward. Now hes made it his mission to help her on her quest to make 100 friends!
(Source: Viz Media)
Inma Tsuihou: Hentai Gift wo Sazukatta Sei de Outo Owareru mo, Onnanoko to "Nakayoku" suru Dake de Chouzetsu Level Up

A world where one's life is decided by one's talent, called a "Gift." The main character, Erio Scarlet, who was born in the house of an influential noble family that had produced a lot of Holy Knights, manifested a suspicious Gift called "Incubus" in the conferment ceremony. Furthermore, the only skill attached to that Gift was one embarrassingly called "Peerless."
Erio was banished from the city because there was no way his indecent existence could be permitted in a family of Holy Knights, but... somehow he went through an amazing growth when he dealt with his horniness?! In addition, when his childhood friend who was bestowed with the Gift "Sacred Knight" chased after him and reverse ra... did it with him, a lot of powerful indecent skills showed up, and on top of that they even got bound by Master-Servant contract...?!
This is the indecent heroic tale of the boy who was gifted with and indecent Gift rising in the world while "getting along" with a lot of girls.
Ushiro no Seki no Gal ni Sukarete Shimatta. Mou Ore wa Damekamoshirenai

Sandai Fujiwara, a socially bottom-tier boy, sits in front of Shino Yuizaki, a beautiful gal at the top of the social caste.
Physically, they are very close to each other, but with their difference in status, it feels like they live in different worlds, never crossing paths with each other.
Until Sandai found Shino stuck in a ditch, having accidentally slipped.
Thanks for the shower
Well, goodbye then.
Although he takes Shino home on a whim to let her shower, Sandai remains wary of the gal. However, he finds himself increasingly attracted to Shino, who despite her looks, is actually not that experienced with men, even as she aggressively approaches him.
After some trouble, the two start dating, and begin to spend their days sweetly flirting with each other.
